   CNN's ''Late Edition With Frank Sesno'' -- Topic: Campaign 2000,
congressional politics and the New York Senate race. Guests: Mark
Fabiani, deputy Gore campaign manager for communications; Karl
Rove, chief Bush campaign strategist; Sens. Don Nickles, R-Okla.,
and Dick Durbin, D-Ill; Mike Murphy, Lazio for Senate campaign
strategist.
</P>
<P>
   ''Fox News Sunday'' -- Topic: Projected budget surplus, tax cuts,
Campaign 2000. Guests: House Majority Whip Tom DeLay, R-Texas;
White House budget chief Jack Lew; Karen Hughes, Bush campaign
communications director; and Ron Klain, senior Gore adviser.
</P>
