<HEADLINE> Cubs 3, Brewers 2, 13 Innings  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   CHICAGO (AP) -- Sammy Sosa hit an RBI single with one out in the
13th inning Saturday to lift the Chicago Cubs to a 3-2 win over the
Milwaukee Brewers.
</P>
<P>
   Ricky Gutierrez drew a one-out walk against Steve Woodard (1-7)
in the 13th and took second on a single by Mark Grace. Sosa hit a
3-2 pitch to left field for the game-winner.
</P>
<P>
   Felix Heredia (5-2) pitched two hitless innings for the victory.
The Cubs won for the ninth time in their last 12 games.
</P>
