<HEADLINE> Thomas Makes Debut as Pacers Coach  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   BOSTON (AP) -- Isiah Thomas coached his first game at any level
Saturday, directing a team of Indiana rookies and free agents in a
75-74 loss to San Antonio in the Shaw's Pro Am Summer League.
</P>
<P>
   ''It was fun,'' said Thomas, hired Thursday to replace Larry
