</P>
<P>
   ''Once you figure out the player's abilities, then I could
manage the game and get guys into positions where they could make a
contribution,'' he said.
</P>
<P>
   Thomas reportedly signed a four-year, $20 million contract, but
terms of the deal have not been released.
